Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,

<% if @reminders.count == 1 %>
Good day! You only have 1 reminder today.
<% else %>
Good day! You have <%= @reminders.count %> reminders today.
<% end %>

<% @reminders.each do |reminder| %>
